      * INITIAL SETTING
     C**                   Z-ADD*DATE     TODAY   80
     C**                   TIME           NOW     60
     C                     TIME           D#TIME
JW2   * SAVE ABVEP51 --------------------------------------
 .   C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN99
 .   C           *IN99     DOWEQ*OFF
 .   C                     READ ABVEP51                  99
 .   C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
 .   C                     Z-ADDTODAY     E1CRDT
 .   C                     Z-ADDNOW       E1CRTM
 .   C                     WRITEABVE51S1
 .   C                     ENDIF
JW2  C                     ENDDO
